title: Coffee Center™ 12 Cup Coffeemaker and Single Serve Brewer (SS-15)
description:
The Coffee Center™ features a fully automatic 12 cup coffeemaker on one side and a single-serve brewer on the other. Sipping solo or serving a crowd, it’s easy to enjoy the gourmet taste you expect from a Cuisinart coffeemaker. Get the best of both worlds in one appliance!

https://www.cuisinart.com/products/coffee_makers/ss-15.html
